    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《井底》是一款2024年3月立项的文字冒险类galgame，题材是“超能力悬疑推理故事”，画风是日系校园风格的</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事主要讲述了女主王语韴作为一个业余“侦探”，遇到各种疑难问题，并在侦探事务所所长天翔及其妹妹天音的帮助下，解决案件的故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏以AVG视觉小说的玩法，通过鼠标点击推进剧情进度以游玩游戏内容，游戏的找那个文本量在20万字左右，游戏内拥有双线结局，玩家们可以通过选择相应的分支事件以体验到自己想要的游戏结局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色介绍：</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331220/extras/9a3328e228d5595c55a1c593ced8e0c8.avif?t=1743773025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331220/extras_big/9a3328e228d5595c55a1c593ced8e0c8.avif?t=1743773025 width=800 height=2487 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331220/extras/5388e5915e2a19274a4bd2e9982b5039.avif?t=1743773025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331220/extras_big/5388e5915e2a19274a4bd2e9982b5039.avif?t=1743773025 width=800 height=1062 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331220/extras/2cb1b9f2f01bf253435569dcfb34311a.avif?t=1743773025\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331220/extras_big/2cb1b9f2f01bf253435569dcfb34311a.avif?t=1743773025 width=800 height=2114 /></span></p></li></ul>",
